option.name: originalContent
option.value:
# Handle line endings automatically for files detected as text # and leave binary files untouched. * text=auto
# The above will handle all files NOT found below # # These files are text and should be normalized (convert crlf to lf) *.java text *.xml text *.properties text *.sql text *.md text *.html text *.css text *.js text
# These files are binary and should be left untouched # (binary is a macro for -text -diff -merge) *.jar binary *.class binary *.db binary
